P3
What is a semantic HTML element?
semantic elements describe the meaning of the content inside of the elemment, not just the way it looks

Reason why we use semantic elements?
Organization

Effects the document object model - How the browser reads or understands the content

Accessibility - allows screen readers to understand the structure and meaning better content

SEO - Search Engine Optimization - how search engines rank well-structured pages - moves then higher in the results

Semantic tags replaced the use of <div> tags
    <div class="header"> vs <header>

